(paratype male, NCSU): 95. Abdomen, lateral view; 96. Abdomen, ventral view, detail of the VIII sternite (indicated); 97. Pygofer, lateral view; 98. Subgenital plate, ventral view. 99–100. Aedeagus and style, respectively, lateral view.
</paragraph>
